Mr. Brady
Mr. Brady

17:21.358 --> 17:22.359
Yes

17:22.359 --> 17:23.361
Here you are.

17:23.361 --> 17:24.862
Oh, bless you, bless you.

17:24.862 --> 17:25.863
And Mrs. Brady.

17:25.863 --> 17:27.365
Thank you.

17:27.365 --> 17:29.367
And now then,

17:29.367 --> 17:33.371
Who, may I ask, is the, uh, spiritual
leader of the community

17:33.371 --> 17:35.373
The Rev.
Jeremiah Brown

17:35.873 --> 17:36.874
Go on,
Reverend.

17:36.874 --> 17:37.875
How are you, Reverend

17:37.875 --> 17:40.378
Will you stand here at my side thank you.

17:40.378 --> 17:41.379
Ahem.

17:42.246 --> 17:44.248
My friends of Hillsboro,

17:45.750 --> 17:49.253
You know why I have come here.

17:49.253 --> 17:52.256
It is not merely to prosecute a lawbreaker,

17:52.256 --> 17:55.760
a young man who has spoken out against the revealed word.

17:55.760 --> 17:57.261
I have come here

17:57.261 --> 17:59.263
because what has happened in a schoolroom in your town

17:59.263 --> 18:00.765
has unloosed a wicked attack

18:00.765 --> 18:03.267
from the big cities of the north.

18:03.267 --> 18:05.770
We did not seek this struggle.

18:05.770 --> 18:07.772
We are simple folk,

18:07.772 --> 18:10.775
who seek only to live in brotherhood and peace,

18:10.775 --> 18:13.277
to cherish our loved ones,

18:13.277 --> 18:15.780
to teach our children the ways of righteousness

18:15.780 --> 18:17.281
and of the lord.

18:17.281 --> 18:20.785
But what would they teach them, these idolaters,

18:20.785 --> 18:23.287
these priests of "evil-ution"

18:23.287 --> 18:24.789
what would they have them do

18:24.789 --> 18:27.291
they would have them measure the distance between the stars

18:27.291 --> 18:30.044
and forget him who holds the
stars in his hands.

18:30.044 --> 18:32.046
they are lost, my friends.

18:32.046 --> 18:35.550
For, I tell you, if man believes he is descended from the beasts,

18:35.550 --> 18:37.552
he must remain a beast!

18:37.552 --> 18:40.054
and as the young wolf turns upon the old,

18:40.054 --> 18:43.558
these innocent ones, corrupted and despairing of salvation,

18:43.558 --> 18:45.560
will turn upon their fathers,

18:45.560 --> 18:48.195
and our land will become a land of sodom and gomorrah

18:48.195 --> 18:50.698
of pestilence, of fire, of hatred and of death.

18:50.698 --> 18:52.199
I disagree.

18:52.199 --> 18:54.201
[Crowd murmuring]

18:54.201 --> 18:55.319
Who are you

18:56.821 --> 18:58.322
Uh, Hornbeck.

18:58.823 --> 19:01.325
E.K. Hornbeck of the Baltimore Herald.

19:01.325 --> 19:02.827
Oh, yeah.

19:02.827 --> 19:04.829
Yes, I know your paper...

19:05.830 --> 19:07.832
and your writings, Sir.

19:07.832 --> 19:09.834
Ladies and gentlemen

19:09.834 --> 19:11.335
my paper is happy to announce

19:11.836 --> 19:13.337
that it is sending two representatives

19:13.838 --> 19:16.340
to, uh, "Heavenly Hillsboro"--

19:16.340 --> 19:18.843
the most gifted reporter in America today--

19:18.843 --> 19:19.844
Myself--

19:19.844 --> 19:20.845
[Crowd laughing]

19:20.845 --> 19:23.347
and the most agile legal mind

19:23.347 --> 19:25.850
of the 20th century--

19:25.850 --> 19:27.985
Henry Drummond.

19:27.985 --> 19:28.986
[Crowd murmuring]

19:28.986 --> 19:29.737
[man]
who's Henry Drummond

19:29.737 --> 19:31.739
We'll send him back to hell!

19:31.739 --> 19:33.741
ride him out on a rail!

19:33.858 --> 19:35.359
Don't let him into town!

19:35.359 --> 19:36.360
Keep him out!

19:36.861 --> 19:38.613
[Everyone yelling]

19:44.001 --> 19:45.503
No, no, no.

19:45.503 --> 19:48.506
I believe we should welcome Henry Drummond.

19:48.506 --> 19:50.508
If the enemy sends his goliath into battle,

19:50.508 --> 19:52.510
it magnifies our cause.

19:53.010 --> 19:56.013
Henry Drummond has stalked the courtrooms of this land

19:56.013 --> 19:57.014
for 40 years.

19:57.014 --> 19:59.517
When he fights, headlines follow.

19:59.517 --> 20:03.521
The whole world will be watching our
victory over Drummond.

20:03.521 --> 20:06.524
If st. george had killed a dragonfly
instead of a dragon,

20:06.524 --> 20:08.025
who would remember him

20:08.025 --> 20:09.527
[Laughing]

20:09.527 --> 20:12.029
We here in Hillsboro have not only the opportunity

20:12.029 --> 20:13.531
to slay the devil's disciple

20:13.531 --> 20:15.533
but the devil himself!

20:15.533 --> 20:18.536
If it's good enough for Brady...

20:18.536 --> 20:20.538
if it's good enough for Brady

20:20.538 --> 20:23.040
if it's good enough for Brady

20:23.040 --> 20:25.042
if it's good enough for Brady

20:25.042 --> 20:27.044
then it's good enough for me

20:27.044 --> 20:29.547
Oh, give me that old time religion

20:29.547 --> 20:31.298
Give me that old time religion

20:31.799 --> 20:33.801
Give me that old time religion

20:34.301 --> 20:35.670
