01:42:49.113 --> 01:42:50.615
Do you ever think about things

01:42:50.615 --> 01:42:52.116
that you do think about

01:42:52.116 --> 01:42:53.618
Isn't it possible

01:42:53.618 --> 01:42:55.620
that it could have been 25 hours

